{"tid":868719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★建造業前期工種開工不足　紮鐵模板面臨凍薪","createTime":"2018-10-19T17:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T07:42:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9fda6f24f99403a31246c663e46f0c90f15939c","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"香港大型基建工程陸續竣工，前期土木工程量減少，數萬名建造業工友可能面臨十年來罕有的凍薪。工聯會轄下香港建造業總工會正與各工種的商會進行加薪談判，據悉，今年加幅最高只有一成，可能惠及機電、水喉及油漆等後期工種，而前期工種如紮鐵、模板及混凝土等因開工不足，可能面臨凍薪，勞資雙方正就調薪拉鋸，料下周初有談判結果，下月一日生效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181020/bkn-20181020000549617-1020_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181020%2Fbkn-20181020000549617-1020_00822_001.html&d=wFyamN%2FazAoqefmseq8hy1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=12947d18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181020/bkn-20181020000549617-1020_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e2ead7cbff4d4f2d48e1ce87d3196cf0b3189cc7","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00ec2625b3b466cc4670829fe7dca36bf435871","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:14:13.000Z","msg":"★[6月29]建造業對人才需求大，年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bydeQS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bydeQS</a>"},{"pid":"ff365f850ea3e56dae77e70bb5964eb5fb1c5a1d","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"建造業對人才需求大，業界<span style=\"color: red;\">年輕人要好好裝備自己，把握機遇</span>，參加技能比賽是其中一個好方法。香港建造業議會（下稱「議會」）日前舉辦「香港建造業青年技能大賽」，設砌磚、細木等6個比賽項目，由行內「老行尊」擔任評審。參賽者都凝神屏氣，在各個項目一較高下，當中最年輕的參賽者只有16歲，更勇奪項目冠軍，令人驚喜！<br />\n<br />\n議會執行總監鄭定寕指，<span style=\"color: red;\">不少年輕人有感建造業發展前景良好，有意加入</span>，未來議會將提供更多培訓課程，及舉辦更多活動提升他們的專業技能。有經驗的師傅則可傳授工藝予年輕人，驅使建造業逐步邁向專業化和科技化，為建造業增添新血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/photo/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180629083334\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180629083334&h=6471a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180629%2Fbkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html&d=wFyamN%2FazAoqefmseq8hy1zEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=84e1d8ba\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180629/bkn-20180629083043780-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b9acdfe8bf4b34d217e37d3ec9d3075823d45eb5","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce347fd9184fa91d692552df73db384708432651","tid":868719,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3deadfa556b019ddafd748611ef1cb9ed588e73","tid":868719,"uid":171788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"Child 登仔 你有本事停到林鄭唔起人工島咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a2ac4dfcf8c33a33503f97e99b5fa45801e275","tid":868719,"uid":30090,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:01:26.000Z","msg":"其實望人衰真係好過望人好？魚蛋論？"},{"pid":"cec1277d6f3af6d342701db525d8a73d51b6b37f","tid":868719,"uid":128210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTi